title: Shuffle Leadership
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: party_affairs
view-if: shuffle_leadership_timer = 0 and difficulty >= 0
on-arrival: month_activities += 1; shuffle_leadership_timer = 8
card-image: img/vorwarts_2.jpg
go-to: advisor_menu

Changing the leadership of the party is painful, but perhaps it is necessary to adapt to changing circumstances.

Removing advisors will increase dissent from their faction of the party, while selecting advisors will increase a faction's strength.

###################### ADVISOR MENU

@advisor_menu
title: Manage advisors.

- @centrist_slot: Center: [+ center_advisor_name +]
- @reformist_slot: Reformist: [+ reformist_advisor_name +]
- @left_slot: Left: [+ left_advisor_name +]
- @labor_slot: Labor: [+ labor_advisor_name +]
- @neorev_slot: Neorevisionist: [+ neorev_advisor_name +]
- @independent_slot: Independent: [+ independent_advisor_name +]
- @done: Done.

@centrist_slot
title: Center advisor slot
go-to: centrist_slot_menu

@centrist_slot_menu
title: Choose a Center advisor.

- #center_advisor
- @advisor_menu: Back.

@reformist_slot
title: Reformist advisor slot
go-to: reformist_slot_menu

@reformist_slot_menu
title: Choose a Reformist advisor.

- #reformist_advisor
- @advisor_menu: Back.

@left_slot
title: Left advisor slot
go-to: left_slot_menu

@left_slot_menu
title: Choose a Left advisor.

- #left_advisor
- @advisor_menu: Back.

@labor_slot
title: Labor advisor slot
go-to: labor_slot_menu

@labor_slot_menu
title: Choose a Labor advisor.

- #labor_advisor
- @advisor_menu: Back.

@neorev_slot
title: Neorevisionist advisor slot
view-if: neorevisionism > 0
go-to: neorev_slot_menu

@neorev_slot_menu
title: Choose a Neorevisionist advisor.

- #neorev_advisor
- @advisor_menu: Back.

@independent_slot
title: Independent advisor slot
go-to: independent_slot_menu

@independent_slot_menu
title: Choose an Independent advisor.

- #nonfactional_advisor
- @advisor_menu: Back.

@done
title: Stop changing advisors.
go-to: root

###################### CENTER ADVISORS

@add_hilferding
title: Rudolf Hilferding
subtitle: Rudolf Hilferding is an economist and one of our chief Marxist theoreticians. {!<br><br>!}[? if difficulty < 0 : Actions - Against Right and Left, Defending Toleration, Fiscal Policy, Economic Democracy ?]
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/HilferdingRudolf.jpg
tags: center_advisor
view-if: hilferding_advisor = 0 and centrists_resign = 0
on-arrival: hilferding_advisor = 1; center_slot = 1; center_advisor_name = "Hilferding"
go-to: advisor_menu

Rudolf Hilferding is now an advisor.

@remove_hilferding
title: Remove Hilferding
view-if: hilferding_advisor = 1
on-arrival: hilferding_advisor = 0; center_slot = 0; center_advisor_name = "Empty"; center_dissent += 5
tags: center_advisor
go-to: centrist_slot_menu

Hilferding has been removed as an advisor. The Centrist faction disapproves.

@add_wels
title: Otto Wels
subtitle: Otto Wels is a long-time party organizer and member of the leadership, serving under Friedrich Ebert. {!<br><br>!}[? if difficulty < 0 : Actions - Clear the Agenda, Party Discipline, The Republican Synthesis ?]
is-card: true
card-image: img/portraits/WelsRudolf.jpg
tags: center_advisor
view-if: wels_advisor = 0 and centrists_resign = 0
on-arrival: wels_advisor = 1; center_slot = 1; center_advisor_name = "Wels"
go-to: advisor_menu

Otto Wels is now an advisor.

@remove_wels
title: Remove Wels
view-if: wels_advisor = 1
on-arrival: wels_advisor = 0; center_slot = 0; center_advisor_name = "Empty"; center_dissent += 5
tags: center_advisor
go-to: centrist_slot_menu

Wels has been removed as an advisor. The Centrist faction disapproves.

@add_muller
title: Hermann Müller
