view-if: muller_advisor = 0 and muller_dead = 0 and centrists_resign = 0
on-arrival: muller_advisor = 1; center_slot = 1; center_advisor_name = "Müller"
go-to: advisor_menu

Hermann Müller is now an advisor.

@remove_muller
title: Remove Müller
view-if: muller_advisor = 1
on-arrival: muller_advisor = 0; center_slot = 0; center_advisor_name = "Empty"; center_dissent += 5
tags: center_advisor
go-to: centrist_slot_menu

Müller has been removed as an advisor. The Centrist faction disapproves.

@add_breitscheid
